WEBVTT

00:17:00.422 --> 00:17:01.572
You are.

00:17:02.028 --> 00:17:05.050
Not because you're culpable
for your emotions,

00:17:05.074 --> 00:17:10.062
but because the actions
and the experiences that you make today

00:17:10.086 --> 00:17:12.911
become your brain's
predictions for tomorrow.

00:17:13.775 --> 00:17:16.641
Sometimes we are responsible for something

00:17:16.665 --> 00:17:19.302
not because we're to blame

00:17:19.326 --> 00:17:22.397
but because we're the only ones
who can change it.

00:17:23.750 --> 00:17:26.175
Now responsibility is a big word.

00:17:26.199 --> 00:17:27.921
It's so big, in fact,

00:17:27.945 --> 00:17:33.484
that sometimes people feel the need
to resist the scientific evidence